title: Episode 181: How To Handle Toxic Sugar Babies On Seeking
description:
Show Notes:

Can You Meet A Healthy Life Partner on Seeking Arrangements or will you keep ending up with toxic sugar babies that will be too difficult to handle?

Dan’s story of his sugar baby relationship gone awry from Seeking… [04:20]
How to decipher between a woman being nitpicky or actually having constructive criticism… [07:20]
“You have a problem paying money for sex!” [10:00]
When a woman says “I love you” while drunk for the first time, does she mean it? [14:06]
How to tell if a woman has Borderline Personality Disorder (BPD)… [14:37]
When a girl your dating barrages you with unfair claims and character attacks that you believe are false, how should you handle it? [15:50]
The strange reason why women will randomly start an argument with you what seems like totally out of the blue… [19:11]
Why a toxic partner will breakup with you, then come running back… [20:55]
How to tell if a woman is aware of  her manipulative behavior… [23:25]
Why is it good to be unpredictable with women? [26:13]
What do women really want? [27:20]
How to be more unpredictable and exciting with women… [32:15]
How to react if a girl you’re dating see’s that you’re still active with your online dating profile…. [34:38]
The best way to react when she says negative shit to you… [40:32]
Should you text a girl you’re dating to explain yourself in an argument and get some feelings off your chest? [45:45]
Is winning an argument with your significant other a victory worth pursuing? [46:20]
How to get your significant other to be more aware of their behavior and work on themselves/get help… [51:43]
How to respond if you’re on a date and girl squeezes your fat in an effort to make fun of you... [55:35]
Crazy story from Rio using “The Cube” [01:01:20]
Student was flaked on earlier in the night, but ended up pulling a model out of the club and banging… [01:03:40]
